revision.text: '''Roseli''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in the [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding an empty plot with at least 1 [[Mago]], at least 1 [[Nanab]], at least 1 [[Magost]] and at least 1 [[Watmel]]. It emits an aura that increases the chance of encountering a wandering Pok√©mon.
